@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eogdsx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.61 * v1)
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.45 - v1 + 0.94) - 0.01) / v0)
    tmp = wp.abs(v2)
    v2 = 0.54
    v1 = (0.90 + 0.34)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.cos(tmp + 0.83) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.60)))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = wp.exp((0.85 - v0))
    data[tid] = v0
